cf.DomainAncillary.count¶

DomainAncillary.count(x)[source]¶
Emulate
f.count(x)

Equality is tested with the domain ancillary’s cf.DomainAncillary.equals method (as opposed to the == operator).

Note that f.count(x) is equivalent to 1 if f.equals(x) else 0.
